          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/413_step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to&nbsp;<strong>tin foil</strong> and place on a baking tray, folding the edges around the tomatoes to collect any juices</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle them with <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>cashew nuts</strong> to the other end and put the tray in the oven for 7 min or until the cashews have coloured slightly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/413_step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/413_step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/413_step-3-x700.jpg",
