          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/413_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable</strong>&nbsp;<strong>stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;in 800ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.6L]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> saffron</strong> to the <strong>stock</strong> and stir well until it&rsquo;s a bright yellow colour</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>cashew nuts</strong> to a chopping board to cool</p>\r\n<p>Reduce the oven temperature to&nbsp;150&deg;C/ 130&deg;C (fan)/ 300&deg;F/ Gas 2 and return the <strong>tomatoes</strong> to the oven until serving, approx. 20-25 min</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
