            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> <br /><br />Cook&nbsp;for 5 min, then add the <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for a further 2 min until the onion has softened<br /><br />Add the <strong>arborio&nbsp;rice</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong> and stir until both are evenly coated in oil and spice</p>",
